          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">An Assembly of Scribes: Meeting with the Authors of Telonian Lore</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nocte</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Feb  1, 2006, 17:17</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=An%20Assembly%20of%20Scribes%3A%20Meeting%20with%20the%20Authors%20of%20Telonian%20Lore&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_41.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/events/printer_41.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=41&cat=26">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
      </tr>
